04 that &ldquo;the <strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">open technique is superior to the laparoscopic technique</span></em></strong> for mesh repair of primary hernias.&rdquo; (NTD &ndash; link to Article). In that article, <strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">recurrence rates</span></em></strong> for primary hernia repair, <strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">using laparoscopic techniques, were over 2 times higher</span></em></strong> than when an open technique was used. Related post-operative complications were also higher in the laparoscopic group. It is fair to note, regarding both techniques, that these results would vary in the hands of surgeons specializing in hernia surgery.<br />\n<br />\nOpen repairs have been associated with slightly more pain immediately after surgery and producing unsightly scarring. However, this pain, if any, quickly subsides, and <strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">when performed by an experienced surgeon, open repairs leave little, to no, permanent scarring</span></em></strong>"},{"pid":"8035d4c73ebab1a2cf7b69852bf78ba9fcc338d6","tid":2059140,"uid":230645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0c0d9191cdd68ad1db27f368e9971603b446d12","tid":2059140,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T00:34:15.000Z","msg":"你唔理佢會唔會惡化？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"唔理都會係到"},{"pid":"d10ca51f6a4a4107be7122cbb5f9a4f1a2db22d3","tid":2059140,"uid":230645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"497de508d29a30c2d34fe10519609f1ced6604c8","tid":2059140,"uid":358248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ca4d6b85628610dbed9fe34f7f2e3de96cc5d73","tid":2059140,"uid":230645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T16:07:55.000Z","msg":"因為我唔太嚴重，有時會脹有時就縮反入去，對日常生活無咩影響。<br />\n去睇公立醫院，醫生講風險時，比最壞既情況嚇一嚇。<br />\n暫時公立有得做傳統開刀，但因為始終開刀範圍都幾大，諗緊做唔做手術。<br />\n有無人試過？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T01:20:41.000Z","msg":"做唔做唔係一個問題 你只可以選做 唔做會自己好返？會唔會越來越嚴重搞到塞住/打結/缺血壞死感染 要做更大手術切更多器官？所以一定要做<br />\n<br />\n至於疤 生仔開刀都有啦 更何況條疤緊要D定命仔緊要 疤都有得搞淡佢的<br />\n<br />\nThe New England Journal of Medicine concluded in 2004 that &ldquo;the <strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">open technique is superior to the laparoscopic technique</span></em></strong> for mesh repair of primary hernias.&rdquo; (NTD &ndash; link to Article). In that article, <strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">recurrence rates</span></em></strong> for primary hernia repair, <strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">using laparoscopic techniques, were over 2 times higher</span></em></strong> than when an open technique was used. Related post-operative complications were also higher in the laparoscopic group. It is fair to note, regarding both techniques, that these results would vary in the hands of surgeons specializing in hernia surgery.<br />\n<br />\nOpen repairs have been associated with slightly more pain immediately after surgery and producing unsightly scarring. However, this pain, if any, quickly subsides, and <strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">when performed by an experienced surgeon, open repairs leave little, to no, permanent scarring</span></em></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"岩既，知道最嚴重風險，到時先做就危險"},{"pid":"2d91befe439e2f22b6baeb6305b25aec073b9c47","tid":2059140,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e22a58214af4128cb768b5ae49d628560dce1c2","tid":2059140,"uid":230645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"300c7cd25fced70c8091176e9e56e3a2b716eaac","tid":2059140,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"做過<br />\n冇特別，條痕好細，又冇人見到，毛都遮住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T16:47:21.000Z","msg":"巴打邊個位小腸氣？開刀位置？疤痕幾長？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"賓洲上小小"}]}